      "span_text": "Although it is efficient to have a (typically small) set E of efficient peers permanently on to help others, most peers should turn off as soon as they have downloaded the file (as also found for the case when peers must be on from time 0 until they finish downloading [CITATION_1] ), and should download it as fast as possible once they turn on."
